@startuml seq_16_participate_in_poll
title Sequence Diagram: UC-16 Participate in Poll

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Poll Controller" as Controller
participant "Poll Service" as Service
participant "Poll Repo" as PollRepo
participant "Vote Repo" as VoteRepo

User -> Frontend: Select poll option(s) & Vote
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/polls/{poll_id}/vote {option_ids}
Controller -> Service: Submit Poll Vote
Service -> PollRepo: Check poll exists and is open
PollRepo --> Service: Poll is valid and open

Service -> VoteRepo: Check existing poll vote for user
VoteRepo --> Service: Existing vote (if any)

alt Single-choice poll & user already voted
    Service -> VoteRepo: Remove prior vote
end

Service -> VoteRepo: Record new selected option(s)
VoteRepo --> Service: Vote recorded

Service -> PollRepo: Update poll option counters
PollRepo --> Service: Counts updated
Service --> Controller: Updated Poll Results
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Display poll results & lock options
@enduml